{"tid":1299110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逃犯條例已壽終正寢, 何必斟酌字眼?","createTime":"2019-07-09T03:48:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T04:22:27.000Z","uid":187285,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"03b97fa9372fc5b451b46a222646c3246902690b","tid":1299110,"uid":187285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:48:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>各位, 如果我地袋住先, 照收貨, 其中一個後果<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係會比政府開到一個先例</span></span><br />\n日後所有議案都可以用五花八門既字眼模混過關<br />\n我地今日鬆懈咁讓一步, 係會比政府反利用返轉頭<br />\n最終用自己拎起既石頭砸自己對隻腳<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭越係去到呢個局面都仲係要斟酌字眼<br />\n係越證明字眼非常重要, 佢唔可以用錯</span></span><br />\n如果有人同你講何必斟酌字眼上分別既時候<br />\n搞清楚係政府斟酌字眼, 並唔淨只市民斟酌緊字眼<br />\n唔好以為政府係無厘頭或者係技窮<br />\n佢依家每一步都行得好小心<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地係一個訴求都依舊無達成</span></span><br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"97037335e83a43d0880e12d186103da99daa8903","tid":1299110,"uid":259700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:03:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2f4c2334ba60ebb2a5b63a53f0cb75f4a545b4d","tid":1299110,"uid":242278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7dc359f1ab7822d9d43456f5bc5b46092ae26a5","tid":1299110,"uid":13118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:22:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}